{"tid":1133251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"救命！機場巴發羊吊","createTime":"2019-05-01T01:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T01:54:10.000Z","uid":79566,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc47b3593f0743c264f641de2a7bf6984ae4822b","tid":1133251,"uid":79566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T01:49:59.000Z","msg":"自問自己係一個顧及別人感受既公德撚<br />\n今朝早機撘機場巴坐後啲念住瞓下，到黃大仙站一車前往珠海既大媽上車C字型咁圍撚住我同我個啊哥，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係一車</span><br />\n<br />\n佢地嘟緊八達通已經開始起鬨緊，之後一坐低我同我啊哥醒撚晒，而且佢地既戰鬥力好強<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Bro <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Me<br />\n:啊哥,不如我一陣學黃子華咁發羊吊，你幫我屌柒佢地呀<br />\n<br />\n我都未開始發羊吊我啊哥已經企左企身<br />\n:<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嘈撚夠未呀！你傾計傾到喊驚咁把撚呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n之後坐格黎個pair 大媽坐車頭:廢事嘈到人吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢坐車頭都冇乜分別<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">啊哥你好Man呀</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"071deee7a1fff758d1bdf21ca46483324031241c","tid":1133251,"uid":246195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T01:54:10.000Z","msg":"啲大陸人幾好禮貌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}